Plan Your Upgrade to Insurance

Before you upgrade, verify a few details about your current org and figure out exactly which release to upgrade to.

Gather and Verify Info About Your Insurance Org
Choose an Upgrade Path for Insurance
Insurance releases are cumulative. That is, the Summer ’24 major release contains everything from the Spring ’24 major release and all of the contents of the Spring ’24 minor releases. Plus it has all of the new features and enhancements for Summer ’24.

You must gather and verify info about your insurance org before choosing an upgrade path for Insurance.
title: Plan Your Upgrade to Salesforce Insurance
